<li><a href="http://www.federalreserve.gov/boarddocs/testimony/2001/20010404/default.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.federalreserve.gov/boarddocs/testimony/2001/20010404/default.htm" rel="nofollow">Testimony of (Federal Reserve) Governor Laurence H. Meyer: Merchant banking</a>, <a href="/wiki/Federal_Reserve_Bank" title="Federal Reserve Bank">Federal Reserve Bank</a></li>
<li>Martin McLaughlin, <a href="http://www.wsws.org/articles/1999/nov1999/bank-n01.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.wsws.org/articles/1999/nov1999/bank-n01.shtml" rel="nofollow">Clinton, Republicans agree to deregulation of US financial system</a>, World Socialist Web Site, November 1, 1999, retrieved on October 9, 2008</li>
</ul>
